## Deployment Steps (After Code Changes)

1. Push changes to GitHub (`git push`)
2. Go to [render.com/dashboard](https://dashboard.render.com)
3. Click **"New" → "Blueprint"**
4. Connect the `Arjit2716/Real-Time-Detection-System` repo
5. Render auto-reads `render.yaml` and creates all 3 services
6. Wait for build (~5 min) → your app is live!

